{"text_id":32624,"tokens":["Theoretical"," physicists"," have"," recently"," proposed"," a"," new"," paradigm",","," called"," the"," S","lings","hot"," mechanism",","," to"," explain"," the"," success"," of"," the"," inflationary"," paradigm","."," In"," this"," model",","," our"," universe"," popped"," into"," existence"," near"," a"," boundary"," of"," another",","," larger"," universe","."," This"," boundary"," has"," a"," highly"," curved"," geometry",","," which"," could"," lead"," to"," fluctuation"," of"," the"," metric"," across"," the"," boundary","."," These"," metric"," fluctuations"," can"," act"," as"," a"," stochastic"," gravitational"," wave"," background"," (","SW","B","),"," which"," seeds"," the"," formation"," of"," structures"," in"," the"," universe","."," We"," calculate"," the"," power"," spectrum"," of"," SW","B"," generated"," in"," the"," S","lings","hot"," model",","," and"," compare"," it"," with"," the"," power"," spectrum"," of"," Pri","mordial"," scalar"," spectrum"," (","PS",")"," calculated"," by"," the"," W","MAP"," team","."," We"," show"," that",","," for"," some"," parameter"," choices",","," the"," SW","B"," and"," PS"," are"," nearly"," identical","."," We"," conclude"," that"," a"," concrete"," realization"," of"," the"," S","lings","hot"," model"," could"," account"," for"," the"," success"," of"," inflation"," without"," the"," need"," for"," fine","-","tuning","."," The"," full"," paper"," is"," available"," here",":"," https","://","arxiv",".","org","/","pdf","/","2","0","0","4",".","1","1","1","6","4",".","pdf"],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}